Package: matr
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Matrices and Machine Learning Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(
            "Chris", "Walker",
            role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
            email = "walkerjameschris@gmail.com"
          ))
Description: A consistent NumPy inspired API for working with matrices in R.
  Contains the most common matrix operations. Incluces implementations for many
  machine learning models designed to operate over R matrices.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
  Rcpp (>= 1.0.11)
Imports:
  tibble,
  purrr,
  withr,
  glue,
  cli
LinkingTo: Rcpp
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
